abstract: >-
  Security framework for AI and agentic systems in DevSecOps: prompt injection defense, agent authorization (Principle of Least Authority), audit trails for non-deterministic systems, model supply chain integrity, AI-assisted development risk controls, and the Auditor Agent architectural pattern. Aligned with NIST AI 100-1 (AI Risk Management Framework), OWASP LLM Top 10, EU AI Act, and CISA AI Roadmap.
keywords:
  - ai-security
  - agentic-systems
  - prompt-injection
  - llm-security
  - nist-ai-100-1
  - owasp-llm-top-10
  - eu-ai-act
  - auditor-agent
